TestForeachCallsGoalPerItem
/ Narrow repro of the "only step 0 applies" class: iterate a 3-item list,
/ call AddProcessed per item, verify all three calls happened.
/ Same shape as builder's BuildGoalCore → ProcessGroup → ApplyStep chain,
/ without the Building/LLM machinery. If this fails, the regression is in
/ the loop.foreach + goal.call dispatch, not in ApplyStep.
- set %items% = ["a", "b", "c"]
- set %processed% = []
- foreach %items%, call AddProcessed item=%x%
- assert %processed.Count% equals 3


AddProcessed
/ Shared-state mutation via list.add proves AddProcessed fired per iteration
- add "x" to %processed%
